{
  "stem": "11593.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We would invite them for Passover Seder, and they were invited-- and they invited us to the-- for Christmas dinner.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was that?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because [? lots ?] [? of them ?] was they're killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember all the schoolboys from my school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only about three of us survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, [CRYING] the activities, we used to-- well, came back from school, we were allowed to practice, you know, athletics.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we took a moment, do our homework.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For some reason, we were trained to read a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- I personally enjoyed reading a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I stayed up late and read.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we attended the movie theaters, attended soccer games and all sports in our spare time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were too young to get into political discussions, but life was quite smooth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- as you know, as I told you, Jewish population were basically mostly businessmen, professional.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You had some tailors and cobblers and shoemakers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the Ukrainians were farmers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Czechs were farmers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Poles, some were farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The majority worked at the government because the government, the mayor, and the police force were all basically Polish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family, in Europe, we were [? very-- ?] in our particular town, we didn't have a yeshiva, but we did have two Orthodox shuls.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So basically, every Jew in our area, I would say 99%, were traditional religious-- observed all the holidays and on Saturdays and Fridays attended the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The non-Jewish population was also religious and attended their churches on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Religion was very well respected by-- by all the total population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had, occasionally, guy that didn't believe in anything, but that was a small minority.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That life went on like this until 1937, when the Hitler machine start expanding.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
